1
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,400
My Highness,

2
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,680
you are finally back.

3
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:15,360
I have been waiting for you here for a long time.

4
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:17,400
Eunuch, what's the rush?

5
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,560
Today, His Majesty is holding a banquet in the palace

6
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:23,240
to entertain distinguished guests from Baishizhou.

7
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,640
Please hurry up and get ready.

8
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,170
Come to the banquet with me.

9
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,320
Slow down.

10
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:37,880
Come in.

11
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,540
Your Ladyship,

12
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,730
I will go and prepare Miss An Li's room.

13
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:52,440
Go.

14
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,280
I kept you in the palace

15
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:58,320
without discussing it with you.

16
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,780
You don't blame me, do you?

17
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,700
What are you talking about, Aunt?

18
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,720
I don't come to the palace often.

19
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,360
I am naturally happy

20
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,560
to be able to accompany you for a few more days.

21
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:10,290
Would you like to live in the palace permanently?

22
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,840
Permanently?

23
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:14,320
If I

24
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,079
intend to train you to be

25
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,960
the future Queen of Yunqiu,

26
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,520
would you be willing?

27
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,360
Look at you, what's the panic?

28
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,079
Becoming the Crown Princess,

29
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:27,010
isn't that the Queen in the future?

30
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:33,680
A-Aunt wants to marry An Li to the Crown Prince?

31
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,090
The Crown Prince

32
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,280
will be established sooner or later.

33
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,079
I only ask you,

34
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:41,560
do you want to be the Crown Princess?

35
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,079
Good child.

36
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,800
As long as you

37
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,840
obediently listen to me,

38
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:54,040
and ascend to the throne in the future,

39
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,520
it will be a glory for our Baishi clan.

40
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:58,880
By the way,

41
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,000
keep this safe.

42
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:03,600
With it,

43
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,040
no one in the palace

44
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,640
will dare to make things difficult for you.

45
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,200
Thank you, Aunt.

46
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,720
Consort Yu asked me to visit Your Highness.

47
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,530
Greetings, Your Highness.

48
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,280
I wonder why

49
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:39,320
Miss An Li is visiting my Yuze Palace.

50
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:41,380
These are the pastries I made myself.

51
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,850
The ingredients

52
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,380
are unique to my hometown.

53
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,159
Because I came to the palace to see my aunt,

54
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,360
I prepared some more.

55
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:50,320
I hope Your Highness will like them.

56
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:52,960
Thank you for your kindness, Miss An Li.

57
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:54,400
These moon persimmon cakes

58
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,640
seem to come from the southeast.

59
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:57,560
Yunqiu

60
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,760
is located in the Central Plains.

61
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,760
It's rare to see such strange products here.

62
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,620
Your Highness is knowledgeable.

63
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:07,100
These moon persimmons are indeed from a corner of Baishizhou.

64
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,440
Baishizhou.

65
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,440
I heard that

66
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,720
the King of Baishi is also a hero.

67
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,080
After submitting to Yunqiu,

68
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,760
he was enfeoffed as the Vassal King of Baishi.

69
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:22,220
My aunt also entered the palace at that time.

70
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:23,800
But

71
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,800
for so many years,

72
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:28,210
His Majesty has never let my aunt visit her hometown.

73
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,320
So I

74
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:33,640
would come and stay in the palace for a few days every few years.

75
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,400
This time,

76
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,280
I might stay longer.

77
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,680
I have something to do today,

78
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,240
so I won't keep Miss An Li.

79
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,540
Then I'll take my leave first.

80
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,960
Ling Xueyue.

81
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,760
You,

82
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,320
what is your name?

83
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,760
Liuxu.

84
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,760
Then who is this person?

85
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:38,040
This little maid Ling Xue Le,

86
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,320
is acting strange today.

87
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:43,570
Could she be having an affair with that guard?

88
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,880
Such a seductive woman

89
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:46,680
staying by His Highness's side,

90
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,760
isn't she a disaster?

91
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,440
This must be Prince Wuyu.

92
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,680
When you came to Xuecang with your father last time,

93
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,280
you were just a little child.

94
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,400
Now,

95
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,810
you have grown into a handsome prince.

96
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,760
At your age,

97
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,380
you are a few years older than our Pingle.

98
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,400
It's time for you to take a wife.

99
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,120
I wonder

100
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,530
if you have someone in mind.

101
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,360
I

102
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,340
am not married yet.

103
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:33,520
As my father's son,

104
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,720
I should prioritize our country,

105
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,720
and focus on the welfare of our people.

106
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,520
I still need to

107
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,799
learn more about governing the country,

108
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,730
so in the future,

109
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,679
I can share my father's burdens.

110
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,680
Good.

111
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,560
Like father, like son.

112
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,040
Of course.

113
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,560
When we grow old,

114
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,770
this great cause

115
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,320
will eventually be handed over to them.

116
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:56,920
Wuyu.

117
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,160
I actually think

118
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,560
he is a perfect match for our Pingle.

119
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,160
Pingle is still young.

120
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,560
As her mother,

121
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,220
why are you in such a hurry?

122
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,280
Speaking of Pingle,

123
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,680
the kings from all countries have taken their seats.

124
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,940
Why isn't she here yet?

125
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,360
This child,

126
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,080
you spoil her too much.

127
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,820
She is becoming more and more unruly.

128
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,410
Don't you spoil her too?

129
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,840
Earlier,

130
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:38,370
she said she went to prepare a gift for you.

131
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,920
Judging by the time,

132
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,660
she should be here.

133
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,000
This child

134
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,380
is naturally naughty.

135
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,000
This time,

136
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,960
I wonder what she is up to.

137
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:51,840
Never mind.

138
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:52,520
Let her be.

139
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:21,600
Is this

140
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,080
Pingle?

141
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:02,160
I present the Dance of Neon Garments and Feathered Clothes.

142
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:05,290
Wishing Father a happy birthday and boundless fortune.

143
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:08,720
May our Xuecang be prosperous and peaceful.

144
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,800
You silly girl,

145
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,440
you are getting more and more unruly.

146
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,160
You even

147
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:15,680
started playing tricks on me.

148
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,760
Father, you exaggerate.

149
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,730
How would I dare play tricks on you?

150
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,720
It's just,

151
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,840
as for my gift,

152
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,240
do you like it?

153
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:26,800
Look at your father's mouth,

154
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:27,840
it hasn't closed.

155
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,760
He must like it very much.

156
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,120
Girl.

157
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,040
You showed up so late.

158
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,920
Hurry up and offer a toast to the kings

159
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:37,720
as an apology.

160
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,640
I obey.

161
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,600
So

162
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:47,360
she played such a trick.

163
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,540
Thank you all, uncles,

164
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:57,440
for attending my father's birthday banquet.

165
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,560
So please do not mind

166
00:12:58,560 --> 00:13:00,200
my arriving late.

167
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:01,580
Bottoms up.

168
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:05,320
To Princess Pingle.

169
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,440
Princess Pingle,

170
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,280
you are so clever and lovely.

171
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,800
It is a blessing for your father and mother.

172
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,040
Thank you, King Jiyu.

173
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,740
I pay my respects to Princess Pingle.

174
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,880
I hope you have been well, Princess.

175
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,400
Brother Wuyu.

176
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,410
It's been years.

177
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:35,080
Brother, you now have an extraordinary bearing,

178
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,480
even better than before.

179
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,040
Thank you for your praise, Princess.

180
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,480
I don't deserve it.

181
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,200
Miss.

182
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,560
I am the hostage prince of the Jiyu Kingdom,

183
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,160
Ji Wuyu.

184
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,840
I've come to visit the First Prince.

185
00:13:47,280 --> 00:13:49,400
The Prince went to pay respects to His Majesty early this morning.

186
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,600
He hasn't returned yet.

187
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,400
May I wait here for a moment?

188
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,400
Please, Prince Wuyu.

189
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:56,160
I'll go make some tea for you.

190
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,320
Xuele.

191
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,600
Are you drawing

192
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:00,760
the palace defense map?
